2880-0|ref=harv|title-link = Madonna: An Intimate Biography}}\n* {{Cite book|last=Taylor|first=Mark C.|authorlink=Mark C. Taylor (philosopher)|title=Nots|publisher=[[University of Chicago Press]]|year=1993|isbn=978-0-226-79131-9|ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book|last=Tetzlaff|first=David|title=Metatextual Girl|publisher=[[Westview Press]]|year=1993|isbn=978-0-8133-1396-2|ref=harv|url=https://archive.org/details/madonnaconnectio00schw}}\n* {{Cite book|last=Victor|first=Barbara|title=Goddess, Inside Madonna|publisher=Cliff Street Books|year=2001|isbn=978-0-06-019930-2|ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book|last=Voller|first=Debbie|title=Madonna: The Style Book|publisher=[[Music Sales Group|Omnibus Press]]|year=1999|isbn=978-0-7119-7511-8|ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book|last=Warren|first=Holly|last2=George|first2=Patricia Romanowski|first3=Patricia Romanowski|last3=Bashe|first4=Jon|last4=Pareles|authorlink4=Jon Pareles|year=2001|publisher=[[Simon & Schuster|Fireside]]|isbn=978-0-7432-0120-9|title=The Rolling Stone Encyclopedia of Rock & Roll|ref=harv|url=https://archive.org/details/rollingstoneency00holl}}\n* {{Cite book|last=Welton|first=Donn|title=Body and flesh: a philosophical reader|publisher=[[Wiley-Blackwell]]|year=1998|isbn=978-1-57718-126-2|ref=harv}}\n*{{citation|last=Zollo|first=Paul|authorlink=Paul Zollo|title=Songwriters on Songwriting|publisher=[[Da Capo Press]]|year=2003|isbn=978-0-306-81265-1}}\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n{{sister project links|display=Madonna|b=no|commons=Madonna (entertainer)|d=Q1744|n=no|q=Madonna (entertainer)|s=no|v=no|wikt=no}}\n* {{Official website}}\n*[https://networthcloud.com/madonna-louise-wikis/ Madonna] on Networthcloud\n* {{AllMovie name|100711}}\n* {{AllMusic|class=artist|id=p64565|label=Madonna}}\n* {{Britannica|355916|Madonna}}\n* {{Curlie|Arts/People/M/Madonna|Madonna}}\n* {{IMDb name|187|Madonna}}\n* {{Rockhall}}\n* {{TCMDb name}}\n\n{{S-start}}\n{{Succession box|\n| before=[[Branko (DJ)|Branko]], [[Sara Tavares]] & [[Mayra Andrade]]\n| 